GBrain Integration
------------------

OpenBrain can package a GBrain CLI binary and ships a GBrain-backed agent
integration. GBrain source is maintained outside this repository under the MIT
License, with OpenBrain integration flowing through the public
`colinagent/gbrain` fork of `garrytan/gbrain`.

